This is the 5620 ped part.
It is  supposed to be identical to the Blit part except
for the device.h file. The differences are of importance in where
to look for the include files (jped.h) and the memory allocation (jsub.c)

Bundles that are exported for Unix V systems are subjected to a sed
script that replaces the appropriate names as specified by
Bob Hutchison (pyuxvv!hutch, PY-2678)

Users on other systems must modify the makefile. Bob suggests
	CC=dmdcc
	CFLAGS=-O
